  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a retrospective analysis of an homogeneous population of patients with
      aggressive B-cell lymphoma and treated upfront with R-CHOP or R-CHOP like regimens to
      reassess the prognostic factors and hopefully to identify more accurate prognostic subgroups
      with a clinical and therapeutical relevance.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
